snippet.textDisplay:
Holy shit, I have so many wrestling stories. My finisher was the Sharpshooter. I jumped off the top bunk and elbow dropped my friend who was sprawled out on a beanbag chair. I hit my dresser with some part of my body, I don't remember. Could've been the head/shoulder area lol.
I once dropped a trailer on my friend, it's one of those 2 wheeled ones and it was in his driveway and I stuck him under the back part of it, then pushed down the other end to lift up the back, then it came back down. Not very hard, wasn't very big. But I think I hit him in the head. He made a big deal out of it.
This other time a girl was beating up my friend (just play fighting, but he was losing). She had the full mount on him (I'm starting to think he was losing on purpose) and was beating him. He asked for help and everyone looked at me, so I did what any rational 12 year old would do. I went full sprint at her, jumped and made my body go sideways in mid air, arms and legs sprawled out, and I somehow expertly ended up giving her a rear naked choke and got her off my friend in one swift motion. I impressed all my friends that day lol.
